channel.title: Megaupload error
channel.description:
When i try to download something from megaupload it gives me this error.
Your IP address 64.12.116.75 has just downloaded 14563324 bytes. Please wait 2 minutes, then try your download again.
If 64.12.116.75 is not your IP address, you may be sharing a proxy or NAT gateway with other users. If you have configured an HTTP proxy in your browser, disable it and try again. If you don't have a proxy configured, using a different download port may bypass your ISP's proxy. If you see your real IP address listed below, please select it, then try your download again:
